#

Blueberry Waffles

25 min
$8.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

WheatDairyEggs

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastBrunchSweet

Description

Fluffy waffles bursting with fresh blueberries, perfect for a delightful breakfast or brunch!

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 1 ½ cups
  • baking powder: 2 tsp
  • sugar: 2 tbsp
  • salt: ½ tsp
  • milk: 1 ¼ cups
  • eggs: 2
  • butter (melted): ⅓ cup
  • fresh blueberries: 1 cup
